---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import icon1 from "../../assets/icons/vol_vel_var.png";
import icon2 from "../../assets/icons/cost_management.png";
import icon3 from "../../assets/icons/security.png";
import icon4 from "../../assets/icons/selection.png";
import icon5 from "../../assets/icons/changing_landscape.png";
import icon6 from "../../assets/icons/specialized_hiring.png";
import bg_img from "../../assets/images/star_links.png";
---

<style>
    .features {
        background-image: url(../../assets/images/star_links.png);
        background-size: cover;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-position: center;
    }

    .item {
        background-color: #121519;
        border-radius: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px 0px #7b7b7b7a;
    }
</style>

<section class="features">
    <div
        class="container section-3 py-5 mt-n3 mt-sm-n2 mt-md-0 my-lg-3 my-xl-4 my-xxl-5"
    >
        <h2
            class="display-5 text-center pt-md-3 pt-lg-4 pb-xxl-2 mt-xl-3 mb-4 mb-sm-5 text-white"
        >
            Do these sound familiar to you?
        </h2>
        <div
            class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-lg-3 gx-4 gy-4 gy-sm-5 pb-md-4 pb-lg-5 mb-2 mb-lg-0 mb-xxl-2"
        >
            <!-- Item -->
            <div class="col item text-center text-sm-start p-4">
                    <Image
                        src={icon1}
                        alt="icon"
                        class="d-inline-block mb-3 mb-lg-4"
                    />
                    <h3 class="h5 mb-2 text-white">Volume, Velocity, Variety</h3>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-white opacity-70">
                        Understanding 3V's of Big data is fundamental to
                        building big data solution. How do I measure, manage and
                        plan?
                    </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item -->
            <div class="col item text-center text-sm-start p-4">
                    <Image
                        src={icon2}
                        alt="icon"
                        class="d-inline-block mb-3 mb-lg-4"
                    />
                    <h3 class="h5 mb-2 text-white">Cost Management</h3>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-white opacity-70">
                        Big Data storage, processing and software licensing cost
                        increases exponentially. How do I keep cost under
                        control?
                    </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item -->
            <div class="col item text-center text-sm-start p-4">
                    <Image
                        src={icon3}
                        alt="icon"
                        class="d-inline-block mb-3 mb-lg-4"
                    />
                    <h3 class="h5 mb-2 text-white">Data Security</h3>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-white opacity-70">
                        Data security is key to organizations survival. Is my
                        data safe from unauthorized access, malware attacks?
                    </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item -->
            <div class="col item text-center text-sm-start p-4">
                    <Image
                        src={icon4}
                        alt="icon"
                        class="d-inline-block mb-3 mb-lg-4"
                    />
                    <h3 class="h5 mb-2 text-white">Tool Selection</h3>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-white opacity-70">
                        Big Data tools pose problem of “Paradox of choices”.
                        What are the right tools for my organisations's data
                        needs?
                    </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item -->
            <div class="col item text-center text-sm-start p-4">
                    <Image
                        src={icon5}
                        alt="icon"
                        class="d-inline-block mb-3 mb-lg-4"
                    />
                    <h3 class="h5 mb-2 text-white">Changing Landscape</h3>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-white opacity-70">
                        It is predicted that Big Data Landscape will continue to
                        change and high velocity. Will my team be able keep up
                        with the pace?
                    </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item -->
            <div class="col item text-center text-sm-start p-4">
                    <Image
                        src={icon6}
                        alt="icon"
                        class="d-inline-block mb-3 mb-lg-4"
                    />
                    <h3 class="h5 mb-2 text-white">Specialized Hiring</h3>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-white opacity-70">
                        Hiring for Big Data and Data Science projects are
                        becoming increasingly difficulty. Will I be able to
                        deliver project on time?
                    </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
